Neckbeard
[[Image:Blind-kittah-sez-u-needz-a-shave.jpg|right|thumb|They really do.]]
[[Image:FurryNeckbeard.jpg|right|thumb|Typical comment made by a neckbeard.]]

A '''Neckbeard''' (also known as a '''neard''', a [[portmanteau]], or the '''bloatee''') is the strange under-the-chin hair growth only seen on [[fat|fatties]], [[weev|drug addicts with a messianic complex]] and [[UNIX]] programmers. It is derived from the "Abe Lincoln" (not to be confused with the [[Sex move#A|sex move]] as the neckbearded have [[virgin|no relation to sex]]). The purpose of this beard is to delineate the [[neck]] from the [[chin]] when the two have merged due to obesity, forming a [[dickneck|bullfrog neck]]. Wearers hope it will make them look like a badass from ''[[Hackers]]'' or ''[[The Matrix]]'', yet it merely reminds observers of fucking chin lack.

A neckbeard is to beards as the comb-over is to hair. It is never, ever [[cool]].

All neckbeards are ''[[Dungeons & Dragons]]''-obsessed losers, and vice versa. [[It is a mystery|It is not known]] at this time whether growing a neckbeard causes one to play ''[[Dungeons & Dragons]]'' or playing ''[[Dungeons & Dragons]]'' causes one to grow a neckbeard.

==Holmesbeard==
[[Image:holmesbeard.jpg|center|thumb|Behold the Holmesbeard!]]


==Chainsaw Beard==
[[Image:Chainsaws.jpg|thumb|CHAIN SAWS!]]

Like the neckbeard, the Holmesbeard is made of hair that does not go very high on the face, but that is where the similarities end. The Holmesbeard is worn by men such as [[John Holmes]], who had a foot-long [[cock]]; made millions by fucking [[over 9000]] [[pussy|bitches]] and teaching them [[bitches don't know|'bout his dick]]; had a foot-long cock; was skinny as a rail; and most badass of all, had a foot-long cock. Hence, Holmesbeard wearers are the extreme opposite of [[you|neckbeards]] and should be confused with real neckbeards [[never|as often as a neckbeard will get you laid]]. Anyone who confounds the two is a [[fucktard]].

